The paper deals with codebook design for channel estimation in millimeter-wave (mmWave) communications, which is a topic related to information theory (cs.IT) and communication (cs.COMM). The use of hybrid precoding structure involves the design of algorithms and systems (cs.SY). The paper also considers the per-antenna power constraint (PAPC), which is a constraint related to networking and internet architecture (cs.NI). Finally, the paper deals with mmWave communications, which is a topic related to multimedia (cs.MM).
